      "text": "builder.goals from \u0027probes/missing/\u0027, write to %goals%",
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "file.read.Build() on a missing literal path emits a non-fatal warning\nvia Channel(\u0022builder\u0022) and still returns the extension as the inferred\ntype. From PLang we can verify the non-fatal half: build succeeds and\ndownstream annotation is \u0022txt\u0022 (file.read.Build() returned, didn\u0027t\nthrow). The channel emission itself is C# territory \u2014 drained by\nStage4_BuildMethodImplsTests.cs via MemoryChannel.",
